/home/vjovanov/c/rhei/docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md:19:  autonomous coding agent.
/home/vjovanov/c/rhei/docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md:21:  agent-specific launch overrides for autonomous execution.
