/home/vjovanov/c/rhei/docs/specs/rhei-programs.spec.md:195:Duration format is the same as `agent_timeout`: `30s`, `5m`, `1h`, `2h30m`. See [Agents Specification — Duration Format](rhei-agents.spec.md#duration-format).
/home/vjovanov/c/rhei/docs/specs/rhei-programs.spec.md:199:Program timeout uses the same SIGTERM → 10 s grace → SIGKILL sequence and the same timeout-transition evaluation as agent timeout. See [Agents Specification — Timeout Behavior](rhei-agents.spec.md#timeout-behavior) for the full step-by-step. The only program-specific differences are:
