/home/vjovanov/c/rhei/docs/specs/rhei-programs.spec.md:204:Timeout transitions fire with `triggeredBy: 'system'`. See [Transitions Specification — Agent Timeout Trigger](rhei-transitions.spec.md#6-agent-timeout-trigger-triggeredby-system) for the transition selection rules.
/home/vjovanov/c/rhei/docs/specs/rhei-programs.spec.md:208:Program stdout and stderr are captured using the same log format and naming conventions as agents. All output is written to `runtime/logs/` relative to the workspace or plan root.
