### RO-012: Callback Invocation, Context, Rejection, Data Passing, Redirects, and Rollback

Spec sections:

- `docs/specs/rhei-callbacks.spec.md` -> `Basic Transition Approval`
- `docs/specs/rhei-callbacks.spec.md` -> `Dependency Validation`
