  6295	         requires a finite timeout. Set `agent_timeout` on the state, on \
  6296	         `models.<id>.agents.{}.timeout`, on `agents.{}.timeout`, or on \
  6297	         `defaults.agent_timeout` in settings.json.",
  6298	        state_name,
  6299	        resolved.agent.id(),
  6300	        resolved.agent.id(),
  6301	        resolved.agent.id(),
