    84	| `program` | string or object | No | The program command to execute in this state. String form runs via shell. Object form specifies `command`, `env`, `working_directory`, and `shell`. Mutually exclusive with `agent`. See [Program States Specification](rhei-programs.spec.md). |
    85	| `program_timeout` | string | No | Maximum time the program may run before being killed (e.g., `10m`, `1h`). Same duration format and timeout handling as `agent_timeout`. See [Program States Specification](rhei-programs.spec.md#timeout-handling). |
