    88	| `mcp_servers` | array | No | MCP servers attached to the agent subprocess for this state. Entries are ids from the `mcp_servers` settings registry or inline server definitions. Individual entries may be marked `optional: true`. See [MCP Servers and Skills](#mcp-servers-and-skills). |
    89	| `skills` | array | No | Agent skills enabled for this state. Entries are ids from the `skills` settings registry or inline skill definitions. Individual entries may be marked `optional: true`. See [MCP Servers and Skills](#mcp-servers-and-skills). |
